729826f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Church Avenue
729826f-a.text:
3994 Victory Boulevard, east side, between Church
Avenue and Burke Avenue, showing an old house which,according
to Butler's 1853 map, belonged to a member of the Decker family.
In 1874 it was owned by B. Decker and in 1898 by W. P. Cannon.
Butler's and Beers's maps of 1853 and 1874 respectively show this
area (Travisville) to have been resided in by numerous members
of the Decker family.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
